IEC 60870-5-104 Client Master Simulator

Complete Simulation of IEC 104 Client as per Protocol Standard including File transfer (Both Monitoring and control direction).

Add up to 50 Client node in the simulator. Every Client node will work independently.

The user can monitor all data Point information, and quality bits. Send all type of commands, parameter activation, file transfer.

* License Perpetual One-time payment, royalty-free Neither license manager nor dongle required

Interoperability:
http://www.freyrscada.com/docs/FreyrSCADA-IEC-60870-5-104-Client-Interoperability.pdf

Download Evaluation Kit - IEC 60870-5-104 Development Bundle:

In the Development Bundle, We included IEC 60870-5-104 Server & Client Simulator, Windows and Linux Software Development Kit.

Video tutorial:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9clfiPrEbls&list=PL4tVfIsUhy1bx7TVjtZnqFB6tbZBhOlJP


Features

	* Multiple Master / Client Simulation
	* In a Single Client(link) simulate Multiple Stations (Common Address)
	* Data Mode, and Test mode connection type available
	* Supports "Select-Before-Operate" SBO or "Direct-execute" command execution modes
	* supports File Transfer, Directory commands
	* Clock synchronization
	* License Perpetual One-time payment, royalty-free Neither license manager nor dongle required
	* Support all type of Typeid, ASDU, APCI, APDU, Command activation and termination commands, support all Cause of transmission (COT), Parameter in control direction.
	* http://www.freyrscada.com/docs/FreyrSCADA-IEC-60870-5-104-Client-Simulator-User-Manual.pdf
	
	

